Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發送
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,變成這樣說實話會讓人焦急
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是一樣好快呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub註釋: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:38.45,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}真城君大笨蛋  「請等我」什麼的一點都不像真城君！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub註釋: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:38.45,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}畢業那天明明回答你了  卻不相信我嗎！？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub註釋: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:38.45,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}下次再發來這樣的短信我會拒收的哦！（笑）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,亞豆…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.94,0:21:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我會懷著你就是女主角的心情努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.34,0:21:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？最高？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.79,0:22:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.33,0:22:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是M嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.99,0:22:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.02,0:22:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然不討厭只用短信互相加油
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.34,0:22:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被亞豆罵了  反而感覺很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.49,0:22:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被罵了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.75,0:22:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有我很喜歡亞豆  現在卻不想見她
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.12,0:22:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.17,0:22:30.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是亞豆也很喜歡最高  也就是說她也想著同樣的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:31.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.63,0:22:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,與其說是M  還不如說是N呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.27,0:22:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,N？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.71,0:22:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自戀者（NARCISSIST）的N
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub註釋: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.71,0:22:38.20,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}ナルシシスト是ナルシスト更正式的說法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.33,0:22:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多了一個SHI吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.01,0:22:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣更正式
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.87,0:22:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來…如此啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.44,0:24:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美保  聲優出道恭喜！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.86,0:24:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  香耶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.16,0:24:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在發表  我的夢想也決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.03,0:24:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.82,0:24:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下集  牆壁和KISS
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.47,0:24:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話說  我也會朝著夢想加油的！
